            <title>带着爹妈去旅行----阿联酋</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4847df010102dsx9.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s6.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4847df01gaedbd8cb80e5" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/middle/4847df01gaedbd8cb80e5&amp;690" WIDTH="690" HEIGHT="517" NAME="image_operate_54601318159231020" /></A><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
今天先发点照片，马上写点游记哈！<br /></P>
